    "extra_instructions": "Hard stop at 4:00pm every day — never schedule past this. Deep work (contracts, financials, documents, regulatory) must go in the 9am–12pm window. Admin tasks (emails, calls, misc) go in afternoon 12pm–4pm slots. Santos and QPME-related tasks are high priority. My schedule runs on a fortnightly cycle — check the notes on each day profile for fixed commitments. Never schedule over Em Work Calls (Mon/Tue 5–8pm). Leave at least 30 minutes free after each scheduled task block."
